{"tid":534576,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"海航節流 員工文具費限20元人幣","createTime":"2018-01-20T03:10:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-20T13:13:26.000Z","uid":6604,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"308d9fd73091d6f15342feed8c483720f8b797ce","tid":534576,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T03:10:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/daily/article/20180120/20280027\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180120%2F20280027&d=uZLgPutlfvzOgorFboHIZ1KzBYqMCiHg3GgvTcrvEuQ%3D&h=3e4d6471\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180120%2F20280027&h=b3fc6f92\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/daily/article/20180120/20280027</a><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】海航主席陳峰承認有資金困難後，彭博報道，海航首席執行官譚向東本周透過內部通告向員工表示，公司今年將大幅削減開支，及要求員工避免不必要的使費。另外，路透引述消息指，美國政府將不會批准海航的投資項目，直至海航釐清其股權架構。<br />\n<br />\n長4頁紙的海航內部通告表示，管理層可配合公司削減開支作出貢獻，如出席外地活動或會議，每人每日開支應限制在3,000元人民幣內；又應避免不必要公幹。湊巧譚向東取消參加達沃斯世界經濟論壇。但海航方面表示，會另外安排其他人參加。<br />\n<br />\n其他削開支方法，包括人事部應控制員工培訓費用及限制花紅金額；行政部門方面，每名員工的文具費用會被限制至最高20元人民幣，鼓勵員工減少影印及節約用水用電。<br />\n<br />\n另一方面，路透報道，美國政府將不會批准海航的任何投資項目，除非海航提供足夠資訊有關該公司的股權架構問題。這代表海航競購對沖基金SkyBridge，及嘉能可石化產品儲存及物流業務的交易將現阻力。海航對報道未作評論<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"560dc0e235ab50189e74d19fe07f2e59517a4c78","tid":534576,"uid":163826,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T04:41:50.000Z","msg":"黃岐山表示一切穩定。放心投資"},{"pid":"42badcb87f03606c674f2c26719b6f4ccb9a0280","tid":534576,"uid":73915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T04:48:01.000Z","msg":"就執得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d66eaea3f945d922c2b1943efde133fd4e00790d","tid":534576,"uid":130105,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T04:58:38.000Z","msg":"出到節流 ，應該死得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9786fbd8918a634d5885d37a61052e952a3c8743","tid":534576,"uid":11454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T05:00:50.000Z","msg":"香港d銀行收唔收得番啟德條爛數？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b71fbe494c1ca351f6d6f7661eadfb9b950bfd18","tid":534576,"uid":37735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9786fbd8918a634d5885d37a61052e952a3c8743","tid":534576,"uid":11454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T05:00:50.000Z","msg":"香港d銀行收唔收得番啟德條爛數？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T05:04:02.000Z","msg":"無聽過胖虎定律<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n黨的錢是黨的  香港銀行的錢都是黨的"},{"pid":"f854a718709584feeb7e76ae9bdd8a09c8107631","tid":534576,"uid":86756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T13:13:26.000Z","msg":"間公司<em></em>做咩工程？"}]}